subject: Rock Climbing
Accidents and Safety
Parachutes and Parachute Jumping
lead_paragraph: After Potter and Graham Hunt leapt off Taft Point, about 3,000 feet above the floor of Yosemite Valley, they tried to clear a notch in the cliffs but smashed into the rocks.
